{"tid":406683,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"晨早搭車最撚憎見到呢啲人","createTime":"2017-09-20T00:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T11:44:05.000Z","uid":96207,"like":832,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb93cbacc9e1614490a0f8b42f3367004846b4ed","tid":406683,"uid":96207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:19:23.000Z","msg":"無論搭巴士定小巴，總係有啲人鍾意坐走廊位，但最仆街係有啲人永遠唔撚識讓開比人入去坐，掛撚住玩手機，好聲好氣同你講句「唔該」你又西口西面。<br />\n<br />\n好撚心你班仆街繁忙時間就醒目啲啦，阻撚住晒，啱啱就大大聲同條友講「喂！唔該呀喂！」跟手條友先尷尷尬尬咁讓比我入去坐<br />\n<br />\n係呀！就係話緊你呀啱啱搭巴士掛住上連登、聽歌，on99無反應果條連登仔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好應該屌死呢班自私撚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關你撚事，照西鳩你面"},{"pid":"4fb32d0eb732f4e52dccafafaadccbef25685cd8","tid":406683,"uid":53798,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:21:04.000Z","msg":"人不嬲自私"},{"pid":"b34bccd6efed3e3e69c6345b6a085cce1796d14b","tid":406683,"uid":96207,"like":57,"dislike":3,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:24:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人<span style=\"color: red;\">不嬲</span>自私</blockquote><br />\n咁唔代表唔駛屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d7ca409a88f8b06ab52874a274a5f072587a93","tid":406683,"uid":61060,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:33:44.000Z","msg":"仲有迫巴士/地鐵果陣勁多人都要起度揭報紙阻鳩住哂果d廢佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ebc448c3f71c43d8a635302593426988708e5a","tid":406683,"uid":143547,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:37:38.000Z","msg":"廢老/小朋友唔插耳機打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日搭巴士見唔少"},{"pid":"502e8b41347f58912c44d6d00dc74a4a99da0971","tid":406683,"uid":2984,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:40:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有迫巴士/地鐵果陣勁多人都