msg":"唔好話搭車 我搭𨋢都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f761c3101989ae1b647fb155c918378bc43b1c","tid":406683,"uid":111006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:23:54.000Z","msg":"好似坐入面會死咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b0eb0a5af00d0d93c6b61a4e0e98bec27495cf","tid":406683,"uid":96207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:24:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開過呢類既post<br />\n比人屌番轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好撚憎人坐小巴雙人位唔撚坐埋邊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/287064/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/287064/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n大卜"},{"pid":"291b30ed65db30a722d66aa0120f9c4685eb2653","tid":406683,"uid":32444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:24:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無論搭巴士定小巴，總係有啲人鍾意坐走廊位，但最仆街係有啲人永遠唔撚識讓開比人入去坐，掛撚住玩手機，好聲好氣同你講句「唔該」你又西口西面。<br />\n<br />\n好撚心你班仆街繁忙時間就醒目啲啦，阻撚住晒，啱啱就大大聲同條友講「喂！唔該呀喂！」跟手條友先尷尷尬尬咁讓比我入去坐<br />\n<br />\n係呀！就係話緊你呀啱啱搭巴士掛住上連登、聽歌，on99無反應果條連登仔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好應該屌死呢班自私撚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關你撚事，照西鳩你面</blockquote><br />\n坐出邊都算，屌你老母擺埋個袋係入邊個位，仆街你霸位咩？行撚到黎都唔撚識拎開個袋係到望望望。"},{"pid":"399aff3ea67b04e56e09a969e2b6ccd658384d9c","tid":406683,"uid":96829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:24:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點為之西口西面？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通要笑住讓位</blockquote><br />\n無表情同西口西面識唔識分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識得啲人長期keep住黑面神樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b22131898349550432ea7d501265b2b4889c3c","tid":406683,"uid":96207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:25:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>開過呢類既post<br />\n比人屌番轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好撚憎人坐小巴雙人位唔撚坐埋邊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/287064/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/287064/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n大卜</blockquote><br />\n我唔你憎人坐走廊位，我係憎啲自私撚，有時啲人同佢講句唔該會好好咁讓比你，甚至有啲會企起身比你入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e71021e3c6344f7b5f9544cab61f7bd6482cdc5","tid":406683,"uid":96207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:28:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點為之西口西面？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通要笑住讓位</blockquote><br />\n無表情同西口西面識唔識分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識得啲人長期keep住黑面神樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇黎係真係唔識分，黑面神咁樣佢會木無表情咁讓比你，我唔覺得係問題<br />\n<br />\n果啲西口西面係讓比你果時，又望下其他地方有無位，又讓完比你啤住你，又係度'接接'聲果啲"},{"pid":"e2c1ad2c2d5ddbc863a77a7dfbb26b47d2f2dcb3","tid":406683,"uid":26507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:31:02.000Z","msg":"琴日朝係旺角站轉荃灣線往中環方向<br />\n有條撚樣企係比人出個綠色箭嘴前面睇漫畫<br />\n個港鐵職員叫佢讓開啲，佢仲屌返條友轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6604395c0c7b375b0e3d54f50d624484ea4241c2","tid":406683,"uid":96829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0